### 4.5 Optional: property-based (`fast-check`)

One paranoid test that exercises the cross-tenant invariant against random strings:

```ts
import fc from "fast-check";

it("for any q, response.tasks all have projectId === url.params.id", async () => {
  await fc.assert(fc.asyncProperty(fc.string({ minLength: 0, maxLength: 200 }), async (q) => {
    const { dev, q3 } = await seedFixture();
    const res = await GET(/* … with q … */);
    if (res.status !== 200) return; // 4xx is fine
    const body = await res.json();
